Covert Messaging Planning

UDP Packet Size messaging
65,507 bytes = max messaging size
28 bytes for ip and other header info
4 numbers
4th - subtract sum from 1000 if higher than 5
    - take sum if 5 or lower
3rd -> 1st - ascii character
Flip byte to get actual message

